Package: dockerz
Version: 2.0.0-1
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Adhbhut Gupta <adhbutg@gmail.com>
Installed-Size: 5033
Depends: docker.io, git, libc6 (>= 2.34)
Recommends: google-cloud-sdk
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/addy-47/dockerz
Description: Smart multi-service Docker builder with change detection
 Dockerz v2.0 is a powerful CLI tool for building and pushing multiple Docker
 images in parallel with advanced smart features. It supports intelligent
 change detection, multi-level caching, and smart build orchestration to
 significantly improve CI/CD pipeline performance.
 .
 Features include:
  - Git change detection for selective builds
  - Multi-level caching (layer, local hash, registry)
  - Smart build orchestration
  - Automatic image name normalization
  - CI/CD integration with file-based interfaces
  - Google Artifact Registry support
